<br>
Mages simply cannot solo PoP mobs efficiently - and in many cases at all.  A charm soloing druid or quad-kiting wizard in PoN can easily earn a yellow per hour in a post-60 level.  A mage is lucky to make a blue.  I fail to see the RvR in this, since a druid's method of soloing has approximately zero risk (where is the risk with snare?).<br>
<br>
